---
import { Gamepad2, Github, Twitter } from "lucide-react";
---

<footer class="border-t border-border bg-muted/30">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      
      {/* Brand & Mission */}
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-extrabold text-xl tracking-tight">
            <div class="bg-primary text-white p-1.5 rounded-lg">
                <Gamepad2 class="w-5 h-5" />
            </div>
            <span>Nerd<span class="text-primary">Ofertas</span></span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
            Monitoramos os preços das principais lojas de hardware e games do Brasil. 
            Nossa missão é garantir que você nunca mais pague caro no seu setup ou console.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-2">
            <a href="#" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"><Twitter class="w-5 h-5" /></a>
            <a href="#" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"><Github class="w-5 h-5" /></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Links Column 1 */}
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground">Explorar</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            <li><a href="/deals" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Ofertas do Dia</a></li>
            <li><a href="/search?q=placa+de+video" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Placas de Vídeo</a></li>
            <li><a href="/search?q=processador" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Processadores</a></li>
            <li><a href="/search?q=console" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Consoles</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Blog & Dicas</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      {/* Links Column 2 */}
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground">Sobre</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Como funciona</a></li>
            <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Privacidade</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terms" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Termos de Uso</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Contato</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-border mt-12 pt-8 text-center text-xs text-muted-foreground">
        <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Nerd Ofertas. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Não somos uma loja. Somos um comparador de preços. Ao clicar e comprar através de nossos links, podemos receber uma comissão.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
